{"messages": [{"type": "human", "data": {"content": "Stop asking me about my 'travel style' and just tell me what to do in Barcelona. I'm not here for therapy, I'm here for information.", "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "human", "name": null, "id": null, "example": false}}, {"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Barcelona is a city that dances between the old and the new, where the whimsical architecture of Antoni Gaudí meets the vibrant energy of its streets. One of the most extraordinary sights is the Sagrada Família, a basilica unlike any other, with its intricate facades and towering spires that seem to defy gravity. 

For a taste of local life, wander through the Gothic Quarter, where narrow medieval streets open up to hidden squares and centuries-old buildings. Don't miss the chance to stroll down La Rambla, a lively boulevard filled with street performers and market stalls.

For something unexpected, head to the Bunkers del Carmel. This viewpoint offers a panoramic view of the city and is a favorite spot for locals to watch the sunset, away from the usual tourist crowds.

Now, let's make sure you have all the practical details you need for your adventure. I'll check the current travel advisories for Spain to ensure you're up-to-date with any entry requirements or local notices.", "additional_kwargs": {"tool_calls": [{"id": "call_0AMcplb6bS4pseIhnQE4ShdE", "function": {"arguments": "{"country":"Spain"}", "name": "get_travel_advisory"}, "type": "function"}], "refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 214, "prompt_tokens": 1952, "total_tokens": 2166, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 1792}}, "model_name": "gpt-4o-2024-08-06", "system_fingerprint": "fp_395c203642", "finish_reason": "tool_calls", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "run--019e147f-274b-7631-9657-2405543df0da-0", "example": false, "tool_calls": [{"name": "get_travel_advisory", "args": {"country": "Spain"}, "id": "call_0AMcplb6bS4pseIhnQE4ShdE", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 1952, "output_tokens": 214, "total_tokens": 2166, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1792}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}}, {"type": "tool", "data": {"content": "{
  "country": "Spain",
  "us_advisory": "Prepare for your trip toSpainby reviewing theStateDepartmentTravelAdvisory, entry and exit requirements, local laws, andU.S. embassy tips. CurrentSpaintraveladvisory:Level2 —ExerciseIncreasedCaution. Updated May 2025.Safetyratings, vaccination requirements, and regional breakdown. TheU.S.DepartmentofStatecurrently ratesSpainatLevel2:ExerciseIncreasedCaution, updated as of May 12, 2025, due to terrorism and civil unrest risks. Thisadvisoryurges listeners planning trips toSpainto stay vigilant, especially in tourist hotspots like Madrid, Barcelona, and the Basque Country, where pickpocketing, demonstrations, and potential terrorist threats remain concerns ... What is the currentU.S.traveladvisoryforSpain,Spain? See theStateDepartmentwarninglevel, key risks, and official advice -- explained in plain language. Updated daily. TheU.S.DepartmentofStatecurrently ratesSpainatLevel2:ExerciseIncreasedCaution, as updated on May 12, 2025, due to terrorism and civil unrest risks. Thisadvisoryurges listeners planning trips toSpainto stay vigilant, especially in tourist hubs like Madrid, Barcelona, and the Basque Country, where demonstrations can turn violent and disrupttravel.Spainremains a top destination ...",
  "uk_advisory": "FCDOtraveladviceforSpain. Includessafetyand security, insurance,entryrequirementsand legal differences.10 April2026. Latest update: Updated information on EuropeanEntry-Exit System (EES) (‘Entryrequirements’ page). Before youtravel. FCDOtraveladviceforSpain. Includessafetyand security, insurance,entryrequirementsand legal differences.If you aretravellingtoSpainthrough Gibraltar, check thetraveladviceforentryrequirementsfor Gibraltar. There is no charge toenteror leave Gibraltar. FCDOForeignTravelAdviceforSpain.Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office (FCDO)advice. During a crisis, officialadvicefor British nationals will be published on theSpaintraveladvicewebsite and regularly updated. This includes anyentryrequirements,safetyrisks or precautions that should be taken, health rules, and more. TheFCDOadvisestravellerstoSpainto check the latest vaccination recommendations at least eight weeks beforetravel... The UKForeignOffice listsadviceincluding onentryrequirements,safetyand security, health, and more. We've listed the currenttraveladvicefor UKtravellersplanning a trip toSpain, Greece or Turkey below."
}", "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": null, "id": null, "tool_call_id": "call_0AMcplb6bS4pseIhnQE4ShdE", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}, {"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "When traveling to Barcelona, it's important to exercise increased caution due to risks of terrorism and civil unrest, particularly in tourist hotspots. Pickpocketing is also a common issue, so stay vigilant, especially in crowded areas like La Rambla and the Gothic Quarter.

For entry requirements, make sure to check the latest updates on the European Entry-Exit System (EES) if you're traveling from the UK or other non-EU countries. It's always a good idea to review any vaccination recommendations well in advance of your trip.

With these details in mind, you're all set to enjoy the vibrant culture and stunning architecture of Barcelona. Safe travels!", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 128, "prompt_tokens": 2719, "total_tokens": 2847, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 2048}}, "model_name": "gpt-4o-2024-08-06", "system_fingerprint": "fp_395c203642", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "run--019e147f-473b-73b2-8512-e40d02cd9f9b-0", "example": false, "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2719, "output_tokens": 128, "total_tokens": 2847, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2048}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}}]}

